I recently had the pleasure of utilizing  the event space at Green Room, and I couldn't be happier with the experience. The event space at Green Room is impressively spacious, making it a perfect choice for hosting a wide range of events. Whether you're planning a birthday party, a corporate gathering, or any other occasion, this venue has the room to accommodate your needs.

What truly stood out, beyond the fantastic event space, was the exceptional service provided by the owners. They were not only super nice but also incredibly helpful and accommodating. Their commitment to ensuring that our event went off without a hitch was truly amazing. They went above and beyond to make our experience enjoyable and stress-free.

I can't emphasize enough how wonderful the owners were, and their dedication to making our event a success was evident from the start. Their professionalism and warm, friendly attitude made the entire process a pleasure.

I am thrilled to have discovered Green Room and would wholeheartedly recommend it to anyone looking for event space in Harlem. I can confidently say that we will be spreading the word to all our friends and family members about this exceptional rental space. Without a doubt, Green Room is our top choice for any event or occasion in the future. It's the perfect place to create unforgettable memories.

A special thanks to Laronn.
